trans-unit.source: Represents a literal code fragment that can be compiled.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en litteral code-fragment kan kompileres.

trans-unit.source: CodeSnippetCompileUnit can represent a literal block of code that is included directly in the source without modification.
trans-unit.target: CodeSnippetCompileUnit kan representere en litteral blokk med kode som er inkludert direkte i kilden uten endring.

trans-unit.source: A CodeSnippetCompileUnit stores a section of code, exactly in its original format, as a string.
trans-unit.target: En CodeSnippetCompileUnit lagres en del av koden, nøyaktig som et vedlegg som en streng.

trans-unit.source: The CodeDOM does not translate literal code fragments.
Literal code fragments are stored and output in their original format.
trans-unit.target: Litteralen kodefragmenter lagres og utdata i det opprinnelige formatet.

trans-unit.source: CodeDOM objects that contain literal code are provided so developers can encapsulate code that is already in the target language.
trans-unit.target: CodeDOM objekter som inneholder litteral kode er angitt slik at utviklere kan omfatter kode som allerede finnes på språket som mål.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A> property contains the literal code fragment as a string.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A>egenskapen inneholder litteral kodefragmentet som en streng.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.LinePragma%2A> property is optional and specifies the position of the code within a source code document.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.LinePragma%2A>egenskapen er valgfri, og angi plasseringen av koden i et kildedokument kode.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.LinePragma%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: If you use this constructor you should also set the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du bruker denne konstruktøren må du også angi den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The literal code fragment to represent.
trans-unit.target: Fragmentet litteral koden til å representere.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line and file information about where the code is located in a source code document.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir informasjon om hvor koden finnes i et kildedokument kode og filen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeLinePragma"></xref> that indicates the position of the code fragment.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeLinePragma"> </xref> som angir posisjonen for code-fragment.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the literal code fragment to represent.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir fragmentet litteral koden til å representere.
